text: Frankie Carroll (born 1970 in Garryspillane, County Limerick) is a retired Irish sportsperson. He played hurling with his local club Garryspillane and was a member of the Limerick senior inter-county team in the 1990s and 2000s. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Garryspillane hurlers Category:Limerick inter-county hurlers Category:Munster inter-provincial hurlers
